---
layout: base.njk
title: Реконструкція будівель в умовах щільної забудови
slug: reconstruction-urban-areas
layout: post
---

<section class="sectionwork post-page">
  <article class="post-article">
    <header class="post-header">
      <h1 class="post-title">{{ title }}</h1>

      <div class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-date">{{ date | date("uk-UA") }}</span>
        <span class="post-sep">•</span>
        <span class="post-author">Хоменко Андрій</span>
      </div>

      {% if description %}
        <p class="post-desc">{{ description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </header>

    {% if image %}
      <div class="post-hero">
        <img src="{{ image }}" alt="{{ title | escape }}">
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="post-content">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
